                <p class="lead text-secondary mb-5 pe-lg-5">
                    Donec tincidunt lacinia diam, eu volutpat est sollicitudin at. Vestibulum ut mi tristi que, vulputate ante quis, tempus enim. Proin quis euismod purus. Suspendisse efficitur aliquam enim sed consequat vulputate ante quis.
                </p>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center flex-wrap">
                    <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary me-4 mb-2">DISCOVER MORE</a>
                    <a href="#" class="d-flex align-items-center text-dark text-decoration-none fw-bold mb-2">
                        <span class="btn-play me-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-play ms-1"></i></span>
                        How it works
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 position-relative">
                <div class="hero-circle mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
